the implementing office/department to coordinate with the CHD  to facilitate the provision of QAC  for the immediate implementation of the  NTP; and  

the CAO to reconcile their records with the NGAs books of accounts and request for the utilization of the remaining balances for other related projects also beneficial for the City’s constituents, if not, remit the remaining cash to the concerned NGA’s so that the accounts can  be closed in both  accounting records.
